quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  76,23,"Lalle, Mũ ne Muka saukar da Alƙur'ãni a gare ka, saukarwa"
  76,24,"Sabõda haka ka yi haƙuri ga hukuncin Ubangijinka, kuma kada ka bi, daga cikinsu, mai zunubi ko mai kãfirci"
  76,25,"Kuma ka ambaci sũnan Ubangijinka, sãfe da maraice"
  76,26,"Daga dare, sai ka yi sujũda gare Shi, kuma ka tsarkake Shi darẽ mai tsawo"
  76,27,"Lalle ne, waɗannan suna son mai gaugãwa (dũniya) kuma suna bari, a bãyansu, wani yini mai nauyi"
  76,28,"Mũ ne Muka halitta su kuma Muka, ƙarfafa halittarsu, kuma idan Mun so, za Mu musanyâ su da wasu mutane kwatankwacinsu, musanyawa"
  76,29,"Lalle ne, wannan wata tunãtarwa ce, saboda wanda ya so ya riƙa hanyar kirki zuwa ga Ubangijinsa"
  76,30,"Kuma, bã zã ku so ba, sai Allah Ya so, lalle ne Allah Yã kasance Masani' Mai hikima"
  76,31,"Yana shigar da wanda Ya so a cikin rahamarsa, kuma azzãlumai, Yã yi musu tattalin wata azãba mai raɗaɗi"